Splitter :
----------
This is a message routing step that splits a message into multiple messages based on a condition.
you can use splitter in scenario where you need to process each part of the message separately or in parallel.

we have 7 types of splitters :
-> EDI Splitter
-> General Splitter
-> The Idoc splitter
-> iterating splitter
-> pkcs#7/cms splitter
-> Tar splitter
-> Zip Splitter


